https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/digits/digits-release-notes/running-digits.html#running-digits


The solution in my particular case was to deactivate Wayland modifying /etc/gdm3/custom.conf WaylandEnable=false



sudo apt remove --purge cuda-*
sudo apt remove --purge nvidia-*
sudo apt install nvidia-driver-410

sudo usermod -aG docker $USER

install nvidia-docker according to link
https://github.com/NVIDIA/nvidia-docker


go to 
ngc.nvidia.com and create account

docker login ncr.io

docker pull nvcr.io/nvidia/digits:18.09

sudo mkdir /data
sudo chmod 777 /data

sudo mkdir /nvidia_ws
sudo chmod 777 /nvidia_ws

nvidia-docker run --name digits -d -p 8888:5000 -v /data:/data -v /nvidia_ws:/workspace:rw nvcr.io/nvidia/digits:18.09
